          | customer_id (PK) |<--------| order_id (PK)     |
          | name             |         | customer_id (FK)  |
          | email            |         | restaurant_id (FK)|
          | phone            |         | driver_id (FK)    |
          +------------------+         | status            |
                                        | delivery_address  |
                                        | payment_method    |
